  "text": "We adopt diffset [CITATION_1] on the prefix tree, so that we only scan the database twice: one for computing the frequent items, and another one for computing the initial diffsets (i.e., sets of transaction IDs). All other frequent itemsets are then computed using the diffsets. We also remark that the first scan of the database also computes the normalized mutual information between the attributes.",
